#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:1
msgid "`DataTables`——基本面数据和宏观经济数据"
msgstr "DataTables — Fundamental and Macroeconomic Data"

#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:3
msgid ""
"基本面数据和宏观经济数据是指反映一个国家或地区经济基本面和宏观经济状况的数"
"据，包括了货币供应量、社会融资规模、国内生产总值、居民消费价格指数、工业品出"
"厂价格指数、采购经理人指数等多个指标。"
msgstr ""
"Fundamental data and macroeconomic data refer to data that reflect the "
"economic fundamentals and macroeconomic conditions of a country or region, "
"including multiple indicators such as money supply, social financing scale, "
"gross domestic product, consumer price index, producer price index, and "
"purchasing managers' index."

