"The Shanghai Interbank Offered Rate (SHIBOR) is the interest rate benchmark "
"in the Shanghai interbank lending market, including multiple interest rate "
"benchmarks such as overnight, 1-week, 2-week, 1-month, 3-month, 6-month, 9-"
"month, and 1-year rates."

