#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:58
msgid "温州民间借贷指数: `wz_index`"
msgstr "Wenzhou Private Lending Index: `wz_index`"

#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:61
msgid ""
"温州民间借贷指数是指温州地区民间借贷市场的利率指数，包括了温州地区民间借贷市"
"场的综合利率指数、民间借贷服务中心利率、小额贷款公司放款利率、民间资本管理公"
"司融资价格、社会直接借贷利率、其他市场主体利率、农村互助会互助金费率、��州地"
"区民间借贷分期限利率（一月期、三月期、六月期、一年期、长期）等多个利率指标。"
msgstr ""
"The Wenzhou Private Lending Index refers to the interest rate index of the "
"private lending market in Wenzhou. It includes multiple interest rate "
"indicators such as the comprehensive interest rate index of the private "
"lending market in Wenzhou, the interest rate of private lending service "
"centers, the lending rate of microfinance companies, the financing price of "
"private capital management companies, the interest rate of direct social "
"lending, the interest rate of other market entities, the mutual aid fund "
"rate of rural mutual aid associations, and the interest rates of private "
"lending in Wenzhou for different terms (one-month, three-month, six-month, "
"one-year, and long-term)."

