msgid ""
"广州民间借贷指数是指广州地区民间借贷市场的利率指数，包括了广州地区民间借贷市"
"场的综合利率指数、小额贷款公司放款利率、民间资本管理公司融资价格、社会直接借"
"贷利率、其他市场主体利率、农村互助会互助金费率、广州地区民间借贷分期限利率"
"（一月期、三月期、六月期、一年期、长期）等多个利率指标。"
msgstr ""
"The Guangzhou Private Lending Index refers to the interest rate index of the "
"private lending market in Guangzhou. It includes multiple interest rate "
"indicators such as the comprehensive interest rate index of the private "
"lending market in Guangzhou, the lending rate of microfinance companies, the "
"financing price of private capital management companies, the direct lending "
"rate of the social sector, the interest rate of other market entities, the "
"mutual aid fund rate of rural mutual aid associations, and the interest "
"rates of private lending in Guangzhou by term (one-month, three-month, six-"
"month, one-year, and long-term)."

