#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:99
msgid ""
"国内生产总值（GDP）是指一个国家（或地区）在一定时期内生产的全部最终产品和劳务"
"的市场价值。GDP是衡量一个国家经济总量的重要指标，也是国家宏观调控的重要参考指"
"标之一。"
msgstr ""
"Gross Domestic Product (GDP) refers to the market value of all final goods "
"and services produced by a country (or region) within a certain period. GDP "
"is an important indicator for measuring a country's total economic output "
"and is also one of the important reference indicators for national "
"macroeconomic control."

#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:101
msgid ""
"国内生产总值表涵盖了GDP的全部值、同比增速、季度值、第一产业、第二产业和第三产"
"业多个构成指标。"
msgstr ""
"The Gross Domestic Product (GDP) table covers the total GDP value, year-on-"
"year growth rate, quarterly value, and multiple constituent indicators of "
"the primary, secondary, and tertiary industries."

