#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:118
msgid ""
"居民消费价格指数（CPI）是指反映一定时期或特定时点居民家庭购买消费品和服务价格"
"水平的变动情况的综合指数。CPI是衡量居民生活水平变动的重要指标，也是国家宏观调"
"控的重要参考指标之一。"
msgstr ""
"The Consumer Price Index (CPI) is a composite index that reflects changes in "
"the price levels of consumer goods and services purchased by households over "
"a specific period or point in time. The CPI is an important indicator for "
"measuring changes in residents' living standards and is also one of the key "
"reference indicators for national macroeconomic control."

#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:120
msgid ""
"居民消费价格指数表涵盖了CPI的全部商品和服务、食品、非食品、工业品、农产品、服"
"务等多个构成指数及其同比、环比变化率。"
msgstr ""
"The Consumer Price Index (CPI) table covers all components of the CPI, "
"including goods and services, food, non-food items, industrial products, "
"agricultural products, and services, as well as their year-on-year and month-"
"on-month change rates."

