#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:138
msgid "工业品出厂价格指数月度数据: `cn_ppi`"
msgstr "Monthly data for the Producer Price Index (PPI): `cn_ppi`"

#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:141
msgid ""
"工业品出厂价格指数（PPI）是指工业企业生产的产品出厂时的价格指数，是衡量工业品"
"价格变动的重要指标。PPI分为生产资料价格指数和生活资料价格指数两大类，生产资料"
"价格指数又分为采掘工业价格指数、原料工业价格指数和加工工业价格指数三个子类��"
"生活资料价格指数又分为食品类价格指数、衣着类价格指数、一般日用品类价格指数和"
"耐用消费品类价格指数四个子类。"
msgstr ""
"The Producer Price Index (PPI) is the price index of products manufactured "
"by industrial enterprises at the time of their ex-factory sale. It is an "
"important indicator for measuring changes in industrial product prices. The "
"PPI is divided into two main categories: the price index of means of "
"production and the price index of consumer goods. The price index of means "
"of production is further divided into three subcategories: the price index "
"of mining industries, the price index of raw material industries, and the "
"price index of processing industries. The price index of consumer goods is "
"further divided into four subcategories: the price index of food, the price "
"index of clothing, the price index of general daily necessities, and the "
"price index of durable consumer goods."

#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:143
msgid ""
"工业品出厂价格指数表涵盖了PPI的全部工业品、生产资料、生活资料多个构成指数及其"
"同比、环比变化率。"
msgstr ""
"The Producer Price Index (PPI) table covers multiple constituent indices of "
"the PPI for all industrial products, means of production, and consumer "
"goods, as well as their year-on-year and month-on-month change rates."

