#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:179
msgid "中国货币供应量: `cn_money`"
msgstr "China's money supply: `cn_money`"

#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:182
msgid ""
"中国货币供应量是中国人民银行发布的一个重要宏观经济指标，是指金融机构向非金融"
"企业和居民提供的各种货币信贷和融资服务的总量。货币供应量统计包括了M0、M1、M2"
"三个指标。"
msgstr ""
"China's money supply is an important macroeconomic indicator released by the "
"People's Bank of China. It refers to the total amount of various monetary "
"credit and financing services provided by financial institutions to non-"
"financial enterprises and residents. Money supply statistics include three "
"indicators: M0, M1, and M2."

#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:184
msgid "中国货币供应商数据表同样涵盖了M0、M1、M2三个指标及其同比、环比变化率。"
msgstr ""
"The China Money Suppliers Data Sheet also covers three indicators: M0, M1, "
"and M2, as well as their year-on-year and month-on-month change rates."

