#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:211
msgid "采购经理人指数月度数据: `cn_pmi`"
msgstr "Purchasing Managers' Index (PMI) Monthly Data: `cn_pmi`"

#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:214
msgid ""
"采购经理指数（PMI），是通过对企业采购经理的月度调查结果统计汇总、编制而成的指"
"数，它涵盖了企业采购、生产、流通等各个环节，包括制造业和非制造业领域，是国际"
"上通用的监测宏观经济走势的先行性指数之一，具有较强的预测、预警作用。 综合PMI"
"产出指数是PMI指标体系中反映当期全行业（制造业和非制造业）产出变化情况的综合指"
"数。"
msgstr ""
"The Purchasing Managers' Index (PMI) is an index compiled by statistically "
"summarizing the results of monthly surveys of corporate purchasing managers. "
"It covers all aspects of corporate procurement, production, and "
"distribution, including both manufacturing and non-manufacturing sectors. It "
"is one of the internationally recognized leading indicators for monitoring "
"macroeconomic trends and has a strong predictive and early warning function. "
"The Composite PMI Output Index is a comprehensive index within the PMI "
"indicator system that reflects the current output changes across all "
"industries (manufacturing and non-manufacturing)."

#: ../../source/manage_data/3. data_tables_50.md:216
msgid ""
"采购经理人指数表涵盖了制造业PMI、非制造业PMI多个构成指数以及和中国综合PMI三个"
"指数。"
msgstr ""
"The Purchasing Managers' Index (PMI) table covers multiple component indices "
"of the Manufacturing PMI, Non-Manufacturing PMI, and the China Composite PMI."

